        <div class="manufature-bg-overlay">
            <h3>MANUFACTURE</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row manufacture-introduce">
        <div class="manufacture-introduce-left col-md-6">
            <h3>Introduce</h3>
            <p>
                In order to provide our customers with Star Anise, Cassia, Incense Powder, Joss Powder and Bamboo Stick containers, we have selected the leading manufacturing partners in Vietnam to ensure the best product quality and the fastest delivery time.
            </p>
